'''ᱦᱟᱸᱥᱫᱟ ᱥᱚᱣᱵᱷᱮᱱᱫᱽᱨᱚ ᱥᱮᱠᱷᱚᱨ''' (ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱑᱙᱘᱓) ᱫᱚ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛᱤᱭᱟ. ᱚᱱᱚᱞᱤᱭᱟ. ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾

==ᱡᱤᱭᱚᱱ==
ᱡᱟ.ᱛ ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ, ᱦᱟᱸᱥᱫᱟ ᱫᱚ [[ᱦᱚᱲ ᱦᱚᱯᱚᱱ]] ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ, ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱫᱚ ᱥᱤᱧᱚᱛ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ [[ᱟ.ᱫᱤᱵᱟ.ᱥᱤ]] ᱛᱷᱚᱠ ᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱢᱤᱫᱴᱟᱝ ᱠᱟᱱᱟ ᱾ ᱚᱱᱟᱛᱮ ᱱᱩᱭᱟᱜ ᱯᱚᱛᱟᱵ ᱠᱚᱨᱮ ᱚᱱᱟ ᱫᱟ ᱚᱞ ᱥᱚᱫᱟᱨ ᱜᱮᱭᱟᱭ ᱾<ref>Ziya Us Salam, '[http://www.frontline.in/the-nation/a-santhal-suppressed/article9873860.ece A Santhal Suppressed]', ''Frontline'' (13 October 2017).</ref> ᱟᱡᱟᱜ ᱠᱟ.ᱦᱱᱤ ᱠᱚ ᱫᱟ ᱠᱷᱟᱴᱚ ᱠᱷᱟᱴᱚᱜᱮ ᱨᱮ ᱦᱚᱸ ᱟ.ᱰᱤ ᱜᱟ.ᱦᱤᱸᱨ ᱩᱭᱦᱟ.ᱨ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱱᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://scroll.in/article/772558/the-tribal-world-strikes-back-at-indian-writing-in-english-through-a-doctor |title=The tribal world strikes back at Indian writing in English through a doctor |work=Scroll |author=Binoo K. John |date=November 30, 2015 |accessdate=August 15, 2018}}</ref> ᱟᱨ ᱫᱷᱚᱨᱚᱢ ᱞᱟ.ᱭ ᱞᱟᱠᱪᱟᱨ ᱠᱚᱨᱮᱱᱟᱜ ᱵᱷᱤᱛᱤᱨ ᱵᱟᱦᱟᱨ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱞᱟᱛᱷᱟ ᱠᱚᱭ ᱥᱚᱫᱚᱨ ᱜᱮᱭᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.livemint.com/Leisure/tlsafHsKkGsFvOzNRp6eGM/Faith-in-the-local.html |title=Faith in the local |work=Livemint |author=Sumana Roy |date=October 17, 2015 |accessdate=August 15, 2018}}</ref> <ref>Sujit Prasad, '[https://antiserious.com/i-am-a-santhal-and-my-opinion-too-should-matter-hansda-sowvendra-shekhar-8b8d226e7153 “I Am a Santhal, and My Opinion Too Should Matter,” says Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar]', ''antiserious.com'' (16 August 2017) [repr. from the ''Boston Coffee House Magazine'' 2014].</ref> ᱦᱟᱸᱥᱫᱟ ᱫᱚ [[ᱨᱟᱱᱪᱤ]] ᱨᱮ ᱡᱟᱱᱟᱢ ᱞᱮᱱᱟᱭ,<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dnaindia.com/lifestyle/books-and-more-hansda-sowvendra-shekhar-is-a-dedicated-doctor-and-writer-2053574 |title=Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar is a dedicated doctor and writer |work=DNA |author=Kaartikeya Bajpai |date=January 18, 2015 |accessdate=August 15, 2018}}</ref> [[ᱜᱷᱟᱴᱥᱤᱞᱟ]] ᱟᱨ [[ᱪᱚᱠᱤᱲᱤᱭᱟ]] ᱨᱮ ᱦᱟᱨᱟ ᱞᱮᱱᱟᱭ, ᱟᱨ [[ᱢᱩᱥᱟᱵᱚᱬᱤ]] ᱟᱥᱲᱟ ᱨᱮ ᱚᱞᱚᱜ ᱠᱟᱱ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref>Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar, '[https://www.thehindubusinessline.com/blink/read/not-just-one/article7460270.ece Not just one]', ''The Hindu Business Line'' (24 July 2015)</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.livemint.com/Leisure/aZ43AhlrXibH0u9vem9p5K/Ghatsila-A-nostalgists-map.html |title=Ghatsila: A nostalgist's map |work=Mint Lounge/Livemint |author=Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar |date=April 23, 2016 |accessdate=August 13, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://indianquarterly.com/black/ |title=Black |work=The Indian Quarterly |author=Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar |date=April–June 2018 |accessdate=August 13, 2018}}</ref> ᱟᱡ ᱵᱟᱵᱟ ᱛᱤᱠᱤᱱ ᱫᱚ [[ᱜᱷᱟᱴᱥᱤᱞᱟ]] ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ [[ᱦᱤᱱᱫᱩᱥᱛᱟᱱ ᱠᱚᱯᱚᱨ]] ᱨᱮᱠᱤᱱ ᱠᱟ.ᱢᱤ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ ᱾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://indianexpress.com/article/express-sunday-eye/playing-with-fire-5334097/ |title=Playing with Fire: Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar on his first children's book |work=The Indian Express |author=Paromita Chakrabarti |date=September 2, 2018 |accessdate=September 2, 2018}}</ref> ᱱᱩᱭ ᱫᱚ [[ᱡᱷᱟᱨᱠᱷᱚᱸᱰ]] ᱥᱚᱨᱠᱟᱨ ᱯᱟᱦᱴᱟ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱢᱤᱫ ᱚᱥᱯᱟᱛᱟᱞ ᱟᱢᱟᱞᱤᱭᱟ. ᱞᱮᱠᱟᱛᱮ ᱠᱟ.ᱢᱤᱭᱟ ᱾ <ref>{{cite web |url=https://scroll.in/article/772558/the-tribal-world-strikes-back-at-indian-writing-in-english-through-a-doctor |title=The tribal world strikes back at Indian writing in English through a doctor |work=Scroll |author=Binoo K. John |date=November 30, 2015 |accessdate=August 15, 2018}}</ref><ref>Sudipta Datta, '[http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/hansda-sowvendra-shekharfighting-a-ban/article19525262.ece Who is Hansda Sowvendra Shekhar, fighting a ban]', ''The Hindu'' (19 August 2017).</ref> ᱒᱐᱑᱗ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱱᱩᱭ [[ᱯᱟᱠᱩᱨ]] ᱨᱮ ᱪᱟ.ᱠᱨᱤ ᱠᱟᱱᱟᱭ ᱾<ref>Ziya Us Salam, '[http://www.frontline.in/the-nation/a-santhal-suppressed/article9873860.ece A Santhal Suppressed]', ''Frontline'' (13 October 2017).</ref>

ᱱᱩᱭ ᱫᱚ ᱯᱩᱭᱞᱩ ᱠᱷᱚᱱ ᱤᱝᱞᱤᱥ ᱛᱮ ᱚᱞ ᱛᱟᱦᱮᱸᱫ, ᱛᱚᱵᱮ ᱥᱟᱱᱛᱟᱲ ᱨᱮᱭᱟᱜ ᱛᱚᱨᱡᱚᱢᱟ ᱠᱚᱭ ᱚᱞ ᱥᱚᱫᱚᱨ ᱜᱮᱭᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://scroll.in/article/838374/eight-melancholic-introspective-poems-by-parimal-hansda-on-being-a-santhal-today |title=Eight melancholic, introspective poems by Parimal Hansda on being a Santhal today |work=Scroll |author=Parimal Hansda |date=August 20, 2017 |accessdate=August 12, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.asymptotejournal.com/nonfiction/shibu-tudu-memories-of-the-kirta-dangra/ |title=Memories of the Kirta Dangra |work=Asymptote |author=Shibu Tudu |accessdate=August 12, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.asymptotejournal.com/nonfiction/shibu-tudu-memories-of-the-kirta-dangra/santhali/ |title=Memories of the Kirta Dangra (Santhali) |work=Asymptote |author=Shibu Tudu |accessdate=August 12, 2018}}</ref> ᱟᱨ ᱦᱤᱱᱫᱤ ᱠᱷᱟᱱ ᱤᱝᱞᱤᱥ ᱛᱮ ᱦᱚᱸᱭ ᱚᱞ ᱜᱮᱭᱟ ᱾<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.thehindu.com/books/i-am-from-the-earth/article19690085.ece |title=I am from the Earth |work=The Hindu |author=Manish Mundra |date=September 16, 2017 |accessdate=August 12, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usawa.in/in-translation/baba-crows-and-black-smoke.html |title=Baba, Crows and Black Smoke |work=Usawa literary Review |author=Ranendra |date=August 2, 2018 |accessdate=August 12, 2018}}</ref>

